    "subtask_body": "Reviewing the current best tour [11,0,7,8,18,16,2,15,14,1,6,19,13,5,12,4,9,17,10,3] at ~492.8. Let me try a few more 3-opt and or-opt moves to see if any improvement is possible.\n\nTry moving city 16(2,3) to between 15 and 2 in reverse: currently 16\u21922\u219215\u219214. What about 2\u219216\u219215\u219214?\nCurrent: 16\u21922(32.3)+2\u219215(14.4)+15\u219214(36.4)=83.1. New: 2\u219216(32.3)+16\u219215(38.0)+15\u219214(36.4)... wait that's the same edges differently ordered. The segment 16,2,15 vs 2,16,15: 18\u219216\u21922\u219215 vs 18\u21922\u219216\u219215: 45+32.3+14.4=91.7 vs 45.3+32.3+38=115.6 \u2014 worse.\n\nTry or-opt: move city 3 to between 9 and 17.\nRemove 3 from ...10\u21923\u219211: saves 10\u21923(34)+3\u219211(63.5)-10\u219211(97.4)=0.1\nInsert 3 between 9 and 17: costs 9\u21923(21.5)+3\u219217(34.4)-9\u219217(29.1)=26.8. Net: -26.7 \u2014 worse.\n\nTry: swap 0 and 7 positions. Tour becomes [11,7,0,8,18,16,2,15,14,1,6,19,13,5,12,4,9,17,10,3].\n11\u21927(29.5)+7\u21920(11.2)+0\u21928(26.9) vs 11\u21920(24)+0\u21927(11.2)+7\u21928(15.8). Old=51, New=67.6 \u2014 worse.\n\nTry: remove (18,16) and (16,2) and insert 16 between 14 and 1:\nRemove 16: saves 18\u219216(45)+16\u21922(32.3)-18\u21922(45.3)=32. Insert between 14 and 1: 14\u219216(73.7)+16\u21921(95.1)-14\u21921(22.6)=146.2. Net: -114.2 \u2014 much worse.\n\nThe tour appears to be a strong local optimum. Estimated length ~492.8, gap from baseline ~16.2%.",
